[[!meta title="BGT Lullaby"]]

* Author: Damien Sykes-Lindley
* Download [Development version][1]

This addon causes NVDA to automatically go to sleep when running BGT games.

Any speech sent to NVDA by the game will still be spoken, as will any dialogs (input fields and messages).

